# 🏗️ Blueprint: Mock MarTech Data Warehouse & API Troubleshooting Lab

This project guide details how to build a fully functional, containerized Marketing Technology (MarTech) pipeline on your virtualized infrastructure. The lab is explicitly engineered to train you in **API log troubleshooting** (using OpenSearch/Kibana), **REST API manipulation** (via Postman/Bruno), and **Raw SQL Data Warehousing** from scratch, with zero prior programming or database experience required.

---

## 🌐 1. System Architecture & Component Mapping

Instead of paying for expensive corporate endpoints, you will host the entire lifecycle of consumer data natively across your server stack.

```
 [ Postman / Bruno ] --------> [ FastAPI Log Generator ]
   (API Manual Tests)               (Ingestion Endpoint)
                                             |
                                             v
  [ OpenSearch Dashboards ] <--------- [ Fluent Bit ]
    (Kibana Log Analysis)           (Telemetry Shipper)
                                             |
                                             v
 [ Raw SQL Query Practice ] <--------- [ PostgreSQL ]
   (DBeaver Browser UI)              (Data Warehouse)

```

### Resource Allocation (Dell R710 Proxmox Host)

* **Base OS Instance:** Ubuntu 24.04 LTS (or Debian 12) running a standard Docker Engine stack.
* **Compute Profiling:** 2 vCPUs, 6 GB RAM, 40 GB SSD Storage allocation.

